item.title: Floor Plans
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Columbia Landing offers beautifully constructed apartment homes featuring one- and two-bedroom floor plans with easy access to peaceful and upbeat outdoor living. All apartment homes support spacious floor plans with entry foyers, washer and dryer, plenty of storage, and a private balcony or terrace so residents can take in breathtaking views. Each apartment home conveniently comes with a fully-equipped kitchen, perfect for enjoying and preparing a big meal and entertaining. Want to bring your furry friend, no worries! Columbia Landing is completely pet-friendly.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Spacious One- and Two- Bedroom Apartment Homes in Columbia, MD

item.title: Amenities
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Columbia Landings apartment and community amenities offer something for everyone any day of the week. Embark on our hiking trails, or take a dip in the refreshing pool that is nearby. In our quiet residential neighborhood, kick your feet up and relax without any worries. Our apartment homes come equipped with a modern kitchen and your very own washer and dryer. Take in a beautiful sight from your own private balcony or terrace. Youll be living in paradise in no time.
Community Amenities: Pool* Tennis Courts* Playgrounds and Hiking Trails Easy access to 1-95, Baltimore, MD and Washington, D.C. 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Quite Residential Neighborhood High-Speed Internet/Cable Available We Recycle!
Apartment Amenities: $99 Security Deposit w/ Standard Approval & Waived Application Fee** Washer/Dryer in Every Apartment Home Fully-Equipped Modern Kitchen Pet-Friendly*** Private Balcony/Terrace
*Community amenities nearby **On select apartments, contact Leasing Office for details ***See Leasing Manager for details

item.title: Photo Gallery
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Looking for an apartment home at an affordable price with a whole lot to offer? Dont worry, Columbia Landing, has got you covered. Call one of our spacious one and two bedroom floor plans your home, sweet, home today! Our location supports all lifestyles and provides just the right balance of convenient and upbeat living! Take a look at our photos and see for yourself why living at Columbia Landing is the right choice for countless reasons. Contact us to schedule a tour and to speak to our friendly leasing team who are always pleased to help you settle in.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Explore what makes living in Columbia, MD so worthwhile.

item.title: Community
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: From fun playgrounds to beautiful hiking trails, Columbia Landings location offers easy access to both Baltimore, MD and Washington, D.C., making it easy to go out and have a fun-filled day. With a pool and tennis courts nearby, residents are able to enjoy nice weather while relaxing and being active. Nestled in an eco-friendly and quiet residential neighborhood, Columbia Landing is the perfect place to settle down.

item.title: Contact Us
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Contact us today and well answer any questions you may have. Our team of leasing professionals are experts in apartment living and are here to guide you to an apartment home that fits your specific needs and wants.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Contact the Columbia Landing Leasing Team today!

item.title: Home Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: At Columbia Landing, youre not only in a location that fosters a welcoming community with countless entertainment, parks, shopping, dining, schools, and employment options to take advantage of, but youre also situated in an area in Columbia, Maryland that begs to be explored with the beauty of nature. Close to the highly-acclaimed Merriweather Post Pavilion and Columbia Mall, everything your heart desires is within reach. Columbia Landings perfect location combined with its spacious apartment homes creates the ideal living experience for all types of lifestyles.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Everything is within reach at Columbia Landing Apartments!
